Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal lagi libur...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.55,0:00:14.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas pesan dari Cecilia, Teal.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku sekalian\Ningin menyapa Dewa Pelindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.33,0:00:20.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku pamit.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anggap saja rumah sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.04,0:00:25.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.51,0:00:30.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tumben Teal sekalem itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa Pelindung!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.84,0:00:39.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah bersabar sesuai perintahmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.46,0:00:42.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan terlalu bersemangat.\NNanti kau pingsan lagi, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, ini Batu Sihir\Nkesukaan Dewa Pelindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barang semahal ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, jangan sungkan, makanlah yang banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin kau membuang jauh-jauh\Npikiran itu, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.71,0:01:06.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begini, Goy benar-benar\Njadi benalu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ditertawakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.02,0:01:12.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Teal sepertinya memang\Nsangat menyukai Goy, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teh ini... enak banget, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena hasil latihanku selama ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.95,0:01:33.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini juga sangat menyenangkan, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.23,0:01:37.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wahai diriku, kau yakin ini yang terbaik?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.57,0:03:11.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku dipanggil kemari?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma Duke yang bisa kuajak\Nkonsultasi asmara.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.75,0:03:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolonglah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar-benar tidak punya teman, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurang ajar!\NAku punya teman, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kali ini kau berulah apa lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang, ini konsultasi asmara.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.94,0:03:37.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini, aku bisa pakai sihir Vanish Wave\Nuntuk menghilang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.93,0:03:45.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku penasaran apa yang dilakukan Cecilia\Nsetelah kami berpisah, jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lambat, terlalu lambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum selesai!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.04,0:04:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu Cecilia berjuang sekeras itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir-pikir,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.62,0:04:06.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,sepertinya aku tidak benar-benar\Nmengenal gadis yang kusukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu membuatku cemas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menjijikkan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.43,0:04:14.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bolehkah aku menangkapmu atas tuduhan\Nmasuk tanpa izin dan penguntitan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal niatku cuma mau curhat soal asmara?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, tapi itu bukan hal yang buruk, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.64,0:04:28.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten bilang suka pada Nona Cecilia,\Ntapi pendekatanmu terlalu lemah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mataku, kau itu pengecut!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Kapten mau terus menjadi\Nteman minum teh selamanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.55,0:04:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa mengenal orang yang disukai,\Nasmaramu takkan berkembang, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duke, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menguntit itu dilarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menguntit?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini warga sipil atau pelaku kriminal?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau datang di saat yang tepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sisanya serahkan saja\Npada orang yang mengenal Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.97,0:05:20.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong beri tahu aku semua hal\Nyang kalian tahu tentang Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.02,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Skornya nol.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, bicaralah dengan benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemarin-kemarin\Nkau bisa bicara normal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.73,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,"Tidak mau. Waktu itu cuma pengecualian."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.35,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Duh, ya sudah, maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.22,0:05:41.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku tak bisa memaksanya bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ini soal Cecilia, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berutang budi\Nkarena kau sudah memberi saran waktu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuceritakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa Cecilia, kurasa Party Pahlawan\Ntakkan pernah terbentuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian sering terluka?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masalah para wanita yang selalu muncul\Ndi sekitar Yuuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.28,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tulisan seorang kesatria saja\Ntak cukup menghentikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.35,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku yang ke sana,\Nsuasana pasti tambah panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, harap tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia selalu menenangkan kekacauan\Nyang dibuat oleh Yuuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Selama perjalanan, Cecilia menangani\Nhampir semua tugas di balik layar."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya bagi tugas, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.62,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kalau bisa, sudah kami lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.62,0:06:40.71,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,"Kami membagi tugas semampu kami.\NAku bagian memasak."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.08,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Oalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu sendiri, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.11,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa memasak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.01,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Lalu, bagaimana dengan Yuuga?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau disuruh mencari bahan makanan,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia malah membawa masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Cecilia bertugas\Nmengumpulkan informasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kesatria kami tak bisa diandalkan\Nuntuk urusan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urusan keuangan juga dipegang Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi Yuuga sama sekali tak berguna?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi masalah-masalah yang Yuuga akibatkan
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,pada akhirnya selalu berujung\Npada menolong orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang Yuuga pahlawannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebaikannya itu tulus.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa sedikit lebih paham soal Yuuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu!\NAku mau tahu soal Cecilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, dia punya julukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Julukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak tahu?\NIni benar-benar karya seni.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kalian\Nsedang membicarakan hal asyik, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencari Mikana\Nkarena ada yang ingin kubicarakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami cuma sedang bernostalgia...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin bernostalgia dengan Mikana.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pelan-pelan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, Raven.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami permisi dulu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa cuma aku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal julukan Cecilia,\Naku tak bisa mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkat pengorbanan mulia Mikana,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku jadi tahu\Napa yang membuat Cecilia marah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, apa kau masih ada waktu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini panti asuhan tempat Cecilia\Nsering melakukan pelayanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada Tuan Kesatria Berdarah Dingin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Kesatria Berdarah Dingin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatria Berdarah Dingin?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Kesatria Berdarah Dingin!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak punya belas kasih sedikit pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian tidak paham arti kata itu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, di mana Bunda Suci?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunda Suci?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa hari ini Bunda Suci tidak datang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin makan kue buatan Bunda Suci!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Tuan Kesatria Berdarah Dingin.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku diam saja saat bertarung,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.62,0:09:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang-orang mulai menganggapku\Nsebagai pria berdarah dingin yang kejam.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi itu asal-usul\NKesatria Berdarah Dingin, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.42,0:09:35.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Julukan Yuuga adalah "Pahlawan Pengelana".
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikana adalah "Sang Pelindung",
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau "Sahabat Sejati".
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.89,0:09:44.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal-usulnya bikin penasaran,\Ntapi Cecilia...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia benci dipanggil Bunda Suci, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kau akan mengetahuinya nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti akan ada kesempatannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.32,0:10:02.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau kau tak tahu apa yang harus\Ndilakukan setelah mengetahuinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daripada itu,\Napa yang akan Youki lakukan sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia masalahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.88,0:10:16.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengenalnya saja sudah bagus, tapi aku ingin\Nbisa lebih dekat dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau kalian ambil\Nmisi permintaan bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.71,0:10:22.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkatmu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Heroine yang terjebak dalam bahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Protagonis yang datang\Nmenyelamatkan dengan keren!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah momen lahirnya cinta\Nyang tak terelakkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.95,0:10:38.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya, "Operasi Aku Juga Protagonis".
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah dapat izin dari Cecilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini, aku akan menunjukkan sisi kerenku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Mikana di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatria itu yang memintaku datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya ada misi mendadak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raven!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa rencananya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau pamer sisi keren pada Cecilia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah punya rencana.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beri tahu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kuberi nilai.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memberi nilai, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.86,0:11:21.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misi kali ini adalah membasmi undead\Nyang bersarang di sebuah wastu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu misi di mana Cecilia\Nbisa sangat bersinar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.24,0:11:24.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, keren banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi aku membayangkan diriku\Njadi tak terkalahkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,30 poin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejam sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bodoh, ya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia itu klerik!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.57,0:11:50.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ahli dalam membasmi undead!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan cuma memikirkan diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terpenting itu\Napa yang dirasakan Cecilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, hari ini biarlah kau dan Cecilia\Nyang jadi penyerang utama.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan jadi pendukung.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian harus bekerja sama mengalahkan musuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.22,0:12:14.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begitu, kalian akan saling percaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh? Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf membuat kalian menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo? Mikana?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan ikut misi hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah, itu sangat melegakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.24,0:12:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku juga\Nmengajak satu orang lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih untuk yang tempo hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo kita berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo cepat\Nkita kalahkan para undead itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah lupa rencananya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku dan Cecilia di barisan depan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikana dan Hapyneth di barisan belakang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setuju?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tak ada suasana horornya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka sudah muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Circle!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagian ini biar aku yang urus.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.93,0:13:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Circle!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia, kau tak lelah?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Circle adalah sihir wajib bagi klerik,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi aku sudah berlatih\Nuntuk meningkatkan efisiensi mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.75,0:14:04.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sebaiknya kau minum air dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau perhatian juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapten memang biasanya begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, mungkin dia tipe yang kalau berpikir\Nterlalu dalam, malah jadi aneh, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggal ruangan ini saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undead tak mungkin berkumpul\Ndi satu tempat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah pasti ada yang memimpin.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bosnya ada di dalam sini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.97,0:14:41.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undead King.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.68,0:14:48.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakai mahkota, gayanya sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia kuat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.41,0:14:55.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan Undead King tak jauh berbeda\Ndari undead biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma dia sedikit lebih pintar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Julukannya tak sesuai\Ndengan kekuatannya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.71,0:15:09.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, wahai arwah malang yang tinggal\Ndi kediaman orang tanpa izin!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kami kembalikan kau ke alam baka!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kalian?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, ada penyusup.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percuma saja memanggil teman,\Nmereka takkan datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu-satunya undead yang tersisa cuma kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.55,0:15:47.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kau cuma tengkorak biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.14,0:15:53.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Parah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.17,0:16:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu.\NAku cuma ingin sedikit iseng...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejam.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biadab.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kujelaskan dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kau, beraninya kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kau,\Nberaninya kau, beraninya kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terima dengan lapang dada, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak berniat melawan lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia, kelihatannya dia sudah pasrah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong akhiri dengan Holy Circle.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau begitu memedulikan mahkota itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa mahkota ini sangat berharga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.60,0:17:17.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak tahu kenapa,\Ntapi ini sangat berharga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat berharga, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.91,0:17:24.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saat masih hidup dulu,\Nkau adalah raja di suatu tempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuantar kau pergi bersama mahkota itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaan ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Heavens Round!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.91,0:18:00.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya sangat nostalgia.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa mendengar suara orang itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau malah menggunakan\Nsihir tingkat tinggi itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.40,0:18:16.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, undead sudah dibasmi, misi selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.\NKalau begitu, ayo kita pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi karena hari ini kau belum bekerja,\NMikana, tolong ajak Hapyneth
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,keliling kediaman ini sekali lagi\Nuntuk memastikan semuanya aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bekerja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tunggu di kereta kuda, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, Cecilia...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bersandar di bahuku?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau mau kugendong saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pinjam bahumu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlalu banyak memakai energi sihir, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.64,0:18:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tadi khawatir... apa aku bisa\Nmenyucikan mahkotanya juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kelihatan senang, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tidak bisa, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.84,0:19:05.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan lari sekuat tenaga\Nsupaya tak ketahuan Mikana dan Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa malah jaga jarak?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada insiden?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, kita berpisah di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, berapa nilaiku?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, kau masih ingat, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana hasilnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.75,0:20:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.\NAnggap saja penilaian tadi tak pernah ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi nilainya nol besar saking buruknya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.01,0:20:08.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu, tapi kurasa ini yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.85,0:20:15.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhentilah memikirkan hal yang tak perlu,\Nberjuanglah seperti biasa saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saranmu terdengar asal-asalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.64,0:20:21.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu saran terbaik yang bisa kuberikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dah, aku pamit duluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga harus berjuang, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Youki, kudengar kau ke panti asuhan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak yang memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau sudah tahu julukanku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.15,0:20:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong, jangan panggil aku\Ndengan julukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan melakukan hal yang kau benci.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bolehkah aku tahu alasannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau tak mau cerita,\Naku takkan memaksa,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.11,0:21:10.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi menurutku julukan itu\Nsangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.66,0:21:17.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kau berbicara dengan Undead King,\Nkau terlihat sangat agung.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi teringat saat di Kastel Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu Cecilia benar-benar seperti Santa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.57,0:21:27.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, rasanya seolah seorang Santa\Nyang mengulurkan tangan kepadaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Santa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, bukan, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alasan aku dipanggil Bunda Suci...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini cerita yang cukup terkenal,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi daripada kau mendengarnya\Ndari orang lain...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.02,0:21:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cecilia itu hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.31,0:21:58.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pintar memasak dan menjahit,\Npandai cari informasi dan mengelola uang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti seorang ibu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.63,0:22:12.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak saat itu, dia mulai memanggilku\N"ibu, ibu" di depan umum.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.14,0:22:14.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jangan tertawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.08,0:22:20.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya anak sebesar itu, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.14,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.33,0:22:23.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah, Youki!
